{"tid":1390502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"瑪嘉烈醫院投訴信：以其人之道，還治其人之身！","createTime":"2019-07-31T07:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:10:40.000Z","uid":295106,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cda4526b8a03de7a7d246cfb74b5621f6ff28b71","tid":1390502,"uid":295106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"Template<br />\n<br />\nmail to: pmh.enquiry@ha.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n九龍荔枝角瑪嘉烈醫院道2-10號<br />\n瑪嘉烈醫院<br />\n<br />\n謝文華行政總監：<br />\n<br />\n報黃： 貴院醫生黃金耀（骨科專科）是日在社交平台帳戶（Facebook: Ky Wong)上，發表咒罵病人言論，包括「大大力打」病人的手腳「斷手斷腳」、「一個不留」等。<br />\n<br />\n上述惡毒言詞出自  貴院醫生之口，不僅令全香港社會震驚，亦大抵可列為全球醫護界之恥。此事不得以「黃的言論純屬個人意見」為辯解，請  貴院馬上革除黃金耀所有職務，以儆效尤。<br />\n<br />\n（聾豬）<br />\n香港市民<br />\n（連登討論區P牌會員）<br />\n2019年7月31日<br />\n<br />\nattachment:<br />\n黃金耀醫生在網上平台失德言論<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A9pv8bt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA9pv8bt.png&h=670fa046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nreference format:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v6FLXV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v6FLXV.png&h=06eb8b0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49672f8d38e14c74b87b6574e5d590a942e5bd55","tid":1390502,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:11:57.000Z","msg":"打石高"},{"pid":"993cd7682abe33d2bd99351b5f4314421b50c73b","tid":1390502,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"可能是講笑，睇埋其他貼確定。"},{"pid":"72a12c1f181b918d261f851e53e9a047b0e86a7d","tid":1390502,"uid":295106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"993cd7682abe33d2bd99351b5f4314421b50c73b","tid":1390502,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"可能是講笑，睇埋其他貼確定。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e19e29fa8bada841148ce92e4087313a6